Durable: NiMH AA rechargeable batteries have a capacity of 600mAh and can be recharged at least 800 times continuously. Save you the cost of buying disposable alkaline batteries and reduce the harm to the environment.

Solar and Standard Charging: These rechargeable NiMH batteries can be charged via solar, If there is not enough sun out, you can also use the universal AA charger to charge your batteries, Using a fast charger is a better choice since it has a large capacity.

Reviewed in the United States on November 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good Batteries for Solar Lanterns/Lights
reviews.reviewText: I am very pleased with these rechargeable batteries. I used them to replace old batteries in solar lanterns for my yard. These came with a decent amount of charge, enough to confirm that the solar lights would work with new batteries (before they are charged up).These NIMH batteries have the right storage capacity to allow the solar lights to work for several hours after dark, perhaps even overnight. This always depends on the sunshine available to charge them during the day.Replacing the batteries is necessary for solar lights occasionally, as rechargeable batteries don't last forever. I had to be careful replacing the battery, as the electronics & wires inside the solar light are fragile.
